▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀
*/
Function GPFILSQB

Local cFiltro	:= ""

If FunName() == "GPEA180" .OR. FunName() == "TCFA040"
	cFiltro += "SQB->QB_CC == '" + AllTrim(aCols[n,_CCUSTO]) + "' .OR. Empty(SQB->QB_CC)"
ElseIf cPaisLoc == "RUS"
	cFiltro += "Empty(SQB->QB_DTEND) .OR. SQB->QB_DTEND >= Date() .OR. SQB->QB_DTEND == CToD('12/31/9999')"
EndIf

cFiltro := "@#" + cFiltro + "@#"

Return(cFiltro)

